name: SPACESHIP (underscoreLu)

SPACESHIP DESCRIPTION:

Fly through space with your spaceship
Avoid the lasers and unlock new skins
Can you get to a score of 50?


CONTROLS:

Move Up - W or Up Arrow

Move Down - S or Down Arrow
